#: ./README.md:block 13 (paragraph)
msgid ""
"We believe public policy and software should be inclusive, usable, open, "
"legible, accountable, accessible and sustainable. This means we need a new "
"way of designing, developing and procuring both the source code and policy "
"documentation."
